# Neura Visual Preservation

When working on the Neura cartoon mascot:

- Do NOT change size, color, shape, style, position, speech, poses, or timing unless the user explicitly asks.
- Do NOT modify `NeuraFigure`, `CartoonArm`, `computeBodyPose`, welcome script, TTS, or layout CSS in `CartoonLivingEntity.tsx`.
- 3D work belongs in `Neura3D*.tsx` only. Hook it up with minimal render-layer wiring in `CartoonLivingEntity.tsx`.
- Match existing SVG dimensions, hex colors, gradients, and proportions exactly in the 3D model.
